# key-word-unicode

## Input

```
名前 hello
clé value

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..24
  ENTRY@0..13
    WORD_KEY@0..6
      WORD@0..6 "名前"
    SPACE@6..7 " "
    LINE_STRING@7..12
      STRING@7..12 "hello"
    NEWLINE@12..13 "\n"
  ENTRY@13..24
    WORD_KEY@13..17
      WORD@13..17 "clé"
    SPACE@17..18 " "
    LINE_STRING@18..23
      STRING@18..23 "value"
    NEWLINE@23..24 "\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..6 "名前",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@7..12 "hello",
            },
        },
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@13..17 "clé",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@18..23 "value",
            },
        },
    ],
}
```

